	year = {2013},
	abstract = {In this research, model reference fuzzy based control is presented as robust controls for IC engine. The objective of the study is to design controls for IC engines without the knowledge of the boundary of uncertainties and dynamic information by using fuzzy model reference PD p lus mass of air while improve the robustness of the PD p lus mass of air control. A PD plus mass of air provides for eliminate the mass of air and ultimate accuracy in the presence of the bounded disturbance/uncertainties, although this methods also causes some oscillation. The fuzzy PD plus mass of air is proposed as a solution to the problems crated by unstability. Th is method has a good performance in presence of uncertainty.},
