	abstract = {To enhance the performance of cognitive engine(CE) and to better realize the intelligent parameters adjusting in cognitive radio(CR) system,a hybrid cognitive engine(HCE) is designed by using multiple artificial intelligent methods synthetically for reasoning,learning,optimization,decision,and so on.Classical CE models and artificial intelligence for CE are analysed.The HCE function architecture block diagram is created,and the working mechanism and technology characteristics of HCE are discussed.The analysis shows that HCE has strong agility and robustness.},
